<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OnePlace - Manage Your Organization with Ease</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* General reset and typography */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* Full-screen video section styling */
        .video-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .video-container video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        /* Hero text over video with better styling */
        .hero-text-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f73ff, #1f38ff);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero-text-box h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-text-box p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero-text-box a button {
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #1f38ff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .hero-text-box a button:hover {
            background-color: #4f73ff;
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Information section */
        .info {
            padding: 60px 20px 40px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #1f38ff;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .services h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        #features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .feature {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            width: calc(33.33% - 40px);
            min-width: 280px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #1f38ff;
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0 20px 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Fullscreen image section */
        .image-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .image-container img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-text-box {
                padding: 40px 20px;
                margin-top: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero-text-box h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .hero-text-box p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .hero-text-box a button {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .feature {
                width: calc(50% - 20px);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-text-box {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }

            .hero-text-box h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .hero-text-box p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .hero-text-box a button {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }

            .feature {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .info p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .services h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <!-- Video Section -->
        <div id="hero" class="video-container">
            <video autoplay loop muted playsinline id="hero-video">
                <source src="images/1place.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>

        <!-- Info Section with Hero Text on Top -->
        <section class="info">
            <div class="hero-text-box">
                <h1>Welcome to OnePlace</h1>
                <p>Manage your organization with ease and complete control</p>
                <a href="/account/login"><button class="btn-primary">Get Started</button></a>
            </div>
            <p>
                Discover the freedom to manage your organization with complete control.
                OnePlace offers you the tools and flexibility to tailor your management
                system to fit your team's unique needs. Join us and start shaping the
                future of your organization today. Enjoy seamless collaboration, intuitive
                organization, and comprehensive control over your projects and tasks.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Services Section -->
        <div class="services">
            <h1>Our Services and Features</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section id="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <img src="/images/project-manager_11445631.png" alt="Project Management Tool">
                <h3>Project Management Tool</h3>
                <p>
                    Our platform provides a comprehensive project management system designed
                    to help you oversee every aspect of your projects effortlessly. With
                    intuitive task assignment, progress tracking, and deadline management,
                    you can ensure that your team stays on track and meets their goals
                    efficiently. Real-time updates and notifications keep everyone informed,
                    facilitating seamless collaboration and ensuring that no detail is
                    overlooked.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature">
                <img src="/images/workflow.jpg" alt="Customizable Workflows">
                <h3>Customizable Workflows</h3>
                <p>
                    OnePlace offers highly customizable workflows to fit the unique needs of
                    your organization. Whether you need a simple task list or a complex
                    multi-step process, our system allows you to design workflows that match
                    your operational requirements. Drag-and-drop functionality makes it easy
                    to adjust and refine processes, enabling your team to adapt quickly to
                    changing priorities and maintain productivity.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature">
                <img src="/images/communication.png" alt="Integrated Communication">
                <h3>Integrated Communication</h3>
                <p>
                    Effective communication is at the heart of successful project
                    management, and our platform integrates a range of communication tools
                    to support your team. From in-app messaging and discussion boards to
                    file sharing and video conferencing, OnePlace ensures that your team can
                    collaborate and share information seamlessly. This integration helps
                    reduce email clutter, keeps conversations contextually relevant, and
                    ensures that important information is always accessible when needed.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Fullscreen Image Section -->
        <div id="image-section" class="image-container">
            <img src="images/home2nd.jpg" alt="Informative image">
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
